The paper deals with the model checking problem for a variant of propositional dynamic logic (PDL) over message passing systems, which involves the use of automata and parity games. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Learning (cs.LG). Among these, cs.LO and cs.PL seem to be the most likely categories, as they are directly related to the study of logic and programming languages, respectively. The other categories are also relevant, as they involve the use of automata and formal languages, which are key tools in the paper.
